steps.instruction:
- In a large pot, heat olive oil over medium heat
- Press ground beef into the oil to make one large patty, let it brown for 8 to 10 minutes
- Stir and break up the meat into crumbles, cook until no longer pink (about 5 minutes)
- Stir in celery, onion and green bell peppers into the beef, cook until the onions are translucent (about 5 minutes)
- Pour in stewed tomatoes, diced tomatoes with green chilies, tomato sauce and water, break apart large chunks of the stewed tomatoes
- Stir in chili seasoning
- Mix in kidney beans and pinto beans, season with salt and pepper to taste
- Bring to a boil then reduce heat to low to simmer for 1 hour
- Mix in vinegar

food.name: Canned Diced Tomatoes with Green Chilies
